Interface ImageCollectionReader.ICallback

Enclosing class:
ImageCollectionReader 
public static interface ImageCollectionReader.ICallback

This interface defines a call back function that is called with the ImageCollectionReader object as parameter. This is used for calling back into the main program by the time all the .json files defining the photo album have been read and parsed.
